{"title":"宣誓——一位新党员的抒情诗","authors":["陈显涪"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一位新党员的抒情诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈显涪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“七·一”，我怀着满腔激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用大江般的浩荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用波涛般的涌激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去掘开心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓词的河堤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幽闭了几十年的春水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直在寻觅真正的归宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，千言万语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对鲜艳的党旗，火红的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把它们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐化作了铿锵的诗句。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇敬、希冀、理解、坚毅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心、追求、奋斗、给予，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成庄严的信仰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成大江的水滴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成诗中的每一个逗号和句号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成灵感的每一次崛起和闪击。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣誓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我举起手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起人类最伟大的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这短短的几分钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把宏愿镌刻在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生中最珍贵的一页……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}